Sanyo Securities to announce new earnings forecast . Sanyo Securities Co Ltd said it would announce a new revision in its earnings forecast at 4 p . m . ( 0700 GMT ) on Wednesday . It had previously revised its earnings forecast in mid - September . A company spokesman did not elaborate on the planned announcement . Another Sanyo Securities spokesman said Sanyo would only revise its earnings forecast for the six months ended September 30 , 1996 . He said Sanyo would not revise its outlook for full - year earnings . On September 19 , Sanyo lowered its parent current profit forecast for the six months to September 30 to 1 . 10 billion yen from its previous forecast of a 4 . 60 billion yen profit . It posted a parent current loss of 13 . 85 billion yen in the same period the previous year . 
